import { Row, Col, Card } from "react-bootstrap";

const BugItem = ({ bug }) => {
  return (
    <Card className="mb-3">
      <Card.Header>
        <Row>
          <Col className="d-flex justify-content-center">{bug.id}</Col>
          <Col className="d-flex justify-content-center">N/A</Col>
          <Col className="d-flex justify-content-center">N/A</Col>
        </Row>
      </Card.Header>
      <Card.Body>
        <Row>
          <Col>
            <Card.Subtitle>Reporter Name:</Card.Subtitle>
            <Card.Text>
              {bug.first_name} {bug.last_name}
            </Card.Text>
          </Col>
          <Col>
            <Card.Subtitle>Report  Date:</Card.Subtitle>
            <Card.Text>
              {bug.month}/{bug.day}/{bug.year}
            </Card.Text>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
            <Col>
            Card</Col>
        </Row>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>
  );
};

export default BugItem;
